# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# VNBOT — Environment Variables Template
# Copy to .env and fill in real values. NEVER commit .env to git.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── General ───
VNBOT_ENV=development                    # development | staging | production
VNBOT_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5173     # frontend URL (CORS, redirects)
VNBOT_LOG_LEVEL=INFO                     # DEBUG | INFO | WARN | ERROR

# ─── Database (SQLite local in 0.1) ───
DATABASE_URL=sqlite+aiosqlite:///./data/vnbot.db
# PostgreSQL (0.3+): postgresql+asyncpg://vnbot:secret@localhost:5432/vnbot

# ─── Auth / Sessions ───
SESSION_SECRET=CHANGE_ME_TO_64_RANDOM_HEX_BYTES    # openssl rand -hex 32
SESSION_COOKIE_NAME=vnbot_session
SESSION_MAX_AGE_SECONDS=86400                       # 24h

# ─── Encryption ───
# Master key for encrypting integration credentials (CredentialRef.encrypted_secret)
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
ENCRYPTION_KEY=CHANGE_ME_BASE64_32_BYTES
ENCRYPTION_KEY_VERSION=1                            # bump on rotation

# ─── LLM Provider (Z.AI chosen — no API key required) ───
LLM_PROVIDER=zai
LLM_ZAI_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/v1
LLM_ZAI_MODEL=glm-4.6
LLM_ZAI_RATE_LIMIT_RPM=30
# LLM_API_KEY=                               # ← NOT needed for Z.AI
# If future provider requires API key, set it here (NEVER in frontend):
# LLM_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# LLM_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# Or fallback to local Ollama (no API key, 120 RPM):
# LLM_PROVIDER=ollama
# LLM_OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1
# LLM_OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.2

# ─── Scheduler ───
SCHEDULER_LOOKAHEAD_DAYS=30              # pre-generate occurrences up to N days
SCHEDULER_TICK_SECONDS=60                # how often to compute upcoming occurrences
SCHEDULER_TIMEZONE=America/Caracas       # default timezone for new users

# ─── Observability (OpenTelemetry) ───
OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=             # leave empty = console exporter
OTEL_SERVICE_NAME=vnbot-api
OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES=vnbot.env=development

# ─── Frontend (Vite — exposed to client, NO secrets here) ───
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
VITE_OTEL_ENABLED=true

# ─── Security headers ───
CSP_REPORT_ONLY=false                    # true = log only, false = enforce
HSTS_MAX_AGE=31536000

# ─── Notifications (Phase 0.1 = mock channel) ───
NOTIFICATION_CHANNEL_DEFAULT=mock        # mock | web_push | email (future)
# For web_push (future):
# VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
# VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=
# VAPID_SUBJECT=mailto:admin@example.com

# ─── File storage (Phase 0.1 = local filesystem) ───
STORAGE_BACKEND=local
STORAGE_LOCAL_PATH=./data/files
# S3/MinIO (future):
# STORAGE_ENDPOINT=http://minio:9000
# STORAGE_BUCKET=vnbot
# STORAGE_ACCESS_KEY=
# STORAGE_SECRET_KEY=
